short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Search Parameter Module for Query Bench

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Query Bench Module - Google contains a collection of Search Parameters for the use with Query Bench.
After installing this Add-on, the Search Parameters can be chosen and customized in the Query Bench Settings Page for the usage in Google web search.
